## 額外重要聲明 — RESEARCH USE ONLY

This software is intended for **research and educational purposes only**.

The drug sensitivity predictions are generated by a machine learning model
trained on cancer cell-line data (GDSC2) and **have NOT been validated for
clinical use**. Predictions must NOT be used as a substitute for professional
medical judgment, diagnosis, or treatment.

All clinical decisions must be made by qualified healthcare professionals
considering individual patient factors including but not limited to:
drug-drug interactions, pharmacokinetics, patient-specific genetic background,
comorbidities, and clinical contraindications.

