## Data Citations

This software relies on the following datasets, each governed by their own
licenses. Please cite them appropriately:

- **GDSC2** (Genomics of Drug Sensitivity in Cancer):
  https://www.cancerrxgene.org/

- **Cell Model Passports** (Sanger Institute):
  https://cellmodelpassports.sanger.ac.uk/

- **PubChem** (NIH): https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/

- **OpenPBTA** (Children's Brain Tumor Network):
  https://github.com/AlexsLemonade/OpenPBTA-analysis
